        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-03-19 19:05:49.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nDan, I looked the other code, It uses rest connection to post the message. Here we use this lib to manage properties dynamically and use MR directly. I could say different add on functionality with different flavor.",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
      {
        "id": "092a2d4c62a0596f90b977fb3f9311b0c9fa81a9",
