        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-03-20 05:34:18.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nI agree with Brinda. The other code does'nt rely on dynamic properties which CDS components require to do and in this commit we allow different type of connection by using MRClient. In my opinion, this code would be much suitable for CDS applications to use.",
